headline: Equinix Opens CN1 Data Center in Chennai to Boost Expansion
summary: EQIX expands in India with CN1, a Chennai data center offering 800 cabinets, low-latency access and hybrid multicloud connectivity.

headline: Crown Castle upgraded at Wolfe on stable contracts, U.S. focus
summary: Investing.com --Wolfe upgraded Crown Castle International to Outperform from Peer Perform, saying concerns around tenant contracts and satellite competition have limited impact on the tower operator, while broader real estate headwinds make the stock more attractive. The brokerage set a price target of $114, implying a total return of 28% by the end of 2026 including dividends.
